Package: orthoviewer
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Orthogonal Brain Viewer for NeuroImaging Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Bradley", "Buchsbaum", email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An interactive Shiny application for viewing neuroimaging data in orthogonal slices.
    Provides spatial compatibility checking, overlay support with automatic resampling,
    and modern UI with GoldenLayout panels. Built on top of neuroim2 for robust
    neuroimaging data handling.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
